tool_description:
Convenient  Mask Layer Image Generation -  Beta
This API generates image mask layers for use in conjunction with AI image editing tools, such as, but not limited to openai DALL·E 2.
name: MaskMaker
title: MaskMaker

api_list.name: grid
api_list.description:
Random grids: Generate random grids of transparent squares or rectangles with varying sizes and transparency.
height and width are required and must be a value between 1 - 10000
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://maskmaker.p.rapidapi.com/grid"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "maskmaker.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
